text: Yannik Oettl (born 19 November 1996) is a German soccer player who currently plays for UCF Knights, at the University of Central Florida (UCF).Yannik Oettl wird Augsburger, fcaugsburg.de, 26 June 2016 ==Career== Oettl made his professional debut for SpVgg Unterhaching on matchday 37, on 16 May 2015, in a 1–0 win against Preußen Münster. His only other appearance for the first team was a 1–0 loss against Rot-Weiß Erfurt. He also made an appearance for the reserve team. Oettl signed with FC Augsburg on 26 June 2015.
